{"search_data": "Andhra PradeshAP Badiki Vastha Scheme 2018 \u2013 Free Bicylces to Class 8th & 9th Girl StudentsAP Badiki Vastha Scheme 2018 \u2013 FeaturesThe important features and highlights of AP Free Bicycle Distribution Scheme are as follows:-School Education Department will gift one free bicycle to each girl student under this scheme.Only the Class VIII and Class IX Girl Students of government schools are eligible for this scheme from this academic year.The primary objective is to retain girls in schools till they complete high school studies i.e Class 10th (X).As per the school records of last academic year, there would be around 1,94,067 girl students in Class 8th and 1,86,715 girls in Class 9th. So, this scheme will benefit 3,80,782 lakh girls in the state.Govt. will support each and every student to realize their dream of quality education.Previous year, this scheme has various flaws in its implementation. Govt. has released funds to procure bicycles for 1.80 lakh Class 9th girl students. But School Education Dept. has distributed only 1 lakh bicycles and uploaded photographs of only 50,000 bicycle distribution in the last academic year.Badiki Vastha Scheme 2018 will resolve the problem of lower enrollment in schools which results in closure and merging of high schools. This year, govt. will focus on successful implementation of this Free Bicycle Scheme to help the govt. school girl students.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}